{"tid":1628374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月6 連登淪陷","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:54:23.000Z","uid":216002,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e16c782a0dcde770177bacb6fc37f4cc95f238","tid":1628374,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"一直以黎 連登都被為眼中釘 因為呢個簡簡單單嘅平台 係呢4個月 好有召號力 而大家每次係發夢日子時 都會比好多資訊 令發夢人士習慣左發夢前都係連登睇風向<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係 依家呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n大家淨係講要裝修 忽視左呢幾日行動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝修先係我地要爭取嘅事咩？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪唔記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n大家咁做 咪令人覺淋病推緊急法係岩囉 因為難聽都要講 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲人只會覺我地搞破壞 </span> 好多人冇連登 唔知咩事嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時就真係我地輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係唔支持 要割 但唔該大家諗下 我地開頭走出黎嘅目的係咩</span><br />\n<br />\n在此 懇請大家 關注呢兩日嘅夢遊日子 而唔係繼續講裝修<br />\n呢4個月嘅努力 唔可以係到化灰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"47a2e31a27b9b9603989d399ffac28477106a40a","tid":1628374,"uid":216002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/STM0M66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSTM0M66.jpg&h=348c95c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee905b7a85045d94066e1ab9bf95f5cc7869092f","tid":1628374,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:32:25.000Z","msg":"真係做野唔會理連登廢Up <br />\n有用先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4472c827010676ff8ca2dcbef8252a37634a6a5","tid":1628374,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yt2LdNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u